  "description": {
    "canonical": "Counter the dread of battle with a song of praise. Enemies cannot hurt your allies while wounded by Evensong's arrows. Kills with Evensong empower ally weapons with Multishot.\r\n\r\nExperience the true power of Jade's Ensemble when Evensong, Cantare, and Harmony sing together.",
    "display": "用赞美之歌来对抗战斗中的恐惧。被晚祷之箭所伤的敌人将无法伤害你的友军。使用晚祷击杀敌人将增强友军的武器的多重射击。\r\n\r\n当晚祷、歌颂与和谐一同奏响时，体验 Jade 之合奏真正的力量。",
